---
title: Maple-Mustard Pork Chops with Brussels Sprouts and Sweet Potato Coins
description: Pork, mustard and maple are culinary best pals for good reason! This oh-so-Canadian combo of maple and mustard on tender pork chops won't let you down. The hearty veggies complement the sweet and zesty glaze perfectly!
